<br/>
<li><a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/2024/10/28/apple-announces-usb-c-magic-accessories/\">Apple Updates Magic Mouse, Magic Keyboard, and Magic Trackpad With USB-C Ports</a></li>
<br/>
<li><a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/2024/10/28/mac-pro-now-comes-with-usb-c-accessories/\">Mac Pro Now Comes With USB-C Accessories, Including Magic Mouse and Keyboard</a></li>
