<br/>
<h2>14-Inch MacBook Pro With M4 Chip</h2>
<br/>
<ul><li><a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/2024/10/29/new-mac-mini-hints-at-macbook-pro-ram/\">A minimum of 16GB of RAM</a> (up from 8GB for the current base model), as already seen with the new iMac and Mac mini</li>
<br/>
<li><a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/2024/10/06/alleged-m4-macbook-pro-unboxing-video/\">Three Thunderbolt 4 ports</a> (up from two Thunderbolt 3 ports on the current base model)</li>
<br/>
